    "As shown on Table 1, dye photosensitizers exhibited a remarkable performance by efficiently harnessing light energy to initiate intricate photochemical processes, facilitating enhanced charge carrier generation and separation for applications ranging from photocatalysis to sustainable environmental technologies.",
